                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Yesterday, 2:15 PM</p>
                </div>
                <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4 py-2">
                    <p class="text-gray-800 font-medium">New exercise added: "Barbell Squat"</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Yesterday, 11:45 AM</p>
                </div>
                <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-500 pl-4 py-2">
